Ok, Files downloaded and unpacked. The result was a folder containing one big .iso file and one small .mds file.

I have never tried to burn a ps2file before, so please help a dumbass. Do I burn the iso-file (and forget about the other one) or what?
Can I use DVD+R to burn with? (Im using Nero)
"Någon som har den som kan dela med sig?" Hjälp till att seeda då!!!

tooTiredtoo:

You're not a dumbass. Everyone has once been a rookie. Anyway, to the question:

Burn with DVDdecrypter, IMGburn, or Alcohol 120%. Very low speed, like 2x as MAX. Especially with EA Games. And if your PS2 is a newer version, then DVD+R works fine (actually, my PS2 only takes DVD+R), but if it's an older machine, then you HAVE TO use DVD-R. And yes, your machine has to be modded (or you can use SwapMagic, but that method sucks, I think).
Kan någon vänlig själ seeda detta superspel, plz.
